logo.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2014-08-21','2020-12-31',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2016-10-03 11:01:30','2016-10-10 05:20:40',NULL),(150,598,2,0,17,'MedicAlert jewellery can provide a lifeline',NULL,NULL,'medicalert-jewellery-can-provide-a-lifeline',0,'When Marge Parsons took an afternoon walk in Victoria Point recently, the stroll ended in a suburb-wide search for her.','<div id=&quot;description&quot; class=&quot;news-description&quot;>\r\n<p>When Marge Parsons took an afternoon walk in Victoria Point recently, the stroll ended in a suburb-wide search for her.</p>\r\n<p>Marge, 85, has Alzheimer&rsquo;s disease and when her carer arrived and couldn&rsquo;t find her, the search began and police were called.</p>\r\n<p>Her daughter, Susan Denne said her mother was wearing two MedicAlert bracelets engraved with her name and her daughters&rsquo; contact numbers when she went missing, and called on community members to become familiar with the MedicAlert emblem, as the medical and identification jewellery often carried potentially life saving information.</p>\r\n<p>Read the full article by Lyn Uhlmann in the <a href=&quot;http://www.redlandcitybulletin.com.au/story/2406449/medicalert-jewellery-can-provide-a-lifeline/?cs=213&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>Local News of the Redland City Bulletin</a></p>\r\n</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,999,'MedicAlert jewellery can provide a lifeline',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-10','2020-12-31',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2016-10-03 11:05:26','2016-10-03 00:37:00','2016-10-03 11:06:47'),(151,598,2,0,17,'MedicAlert jewellery can provide a lifeline',NULL,NULL,'medicalert-jewellery-can-provide-a-lifeline',0,'When Marge Parsons took an afternoon walk in Victoria Point recently, the stroll ended in a suburb-wide search for her.','<div id=&quot;description&quot; class=&quot;news-description&quot;>\r\n<p>When Marge Parsons took an afternoon walk in Victoria Point recently, the stroll ended in a suburb-wide search for her.</p>\r\n<p>Mar