t;allowfullscreen&quot;></iframe></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h6>*Conditions Apply: Seniors Card discount is applicable to this offer. Not to be used in conjunction with any other offer. No further discounts/offers apply.</h6>','<h2>Why do seniors need medical jewellery?</h2>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re a senior living with a medical condition, medical jewellery could mean the difference between life or death in an emergency. It can speak for you when you can&rsquo;t communicate your needs or condition and will provide your loved ones with piece of mind. Medical alert jewellery helps emergency responders and other first aid workers within the community assist you faster. That&rsquo;s why for seniors, a globally recognised medical alert bracelet, necklace or wristband tag is extremely important.</p>\r\n<p>Medical professionals are trained to look for this type of jewellery when assessing a patient, to find out vital information about their medical history and any condition they may have. A medical ID can protect you if you&rsquo;re out and about, living away from your family members or planning to travel during retirement by ensuring that your medical information is accessible at all times. Wearing medical jewellery will help protect you if you&rsquo;re unable to speak for yourself, or if you&rsquo;re with others who are unaware of your medical conditions.</p>\r\n<p>A MedicAlert medical ID is not just a convenience but a necessity for seniors.</p>','<div id=&quot;redeem&quot;>\r\n<div class=&quot;row&quot;>\r\n<div id=&quot;joinhead&quot; class=&quot;col-sm-12 text-center&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 0;&quot;>A special offer for seniors:<br /> <span class=&quot;highlight&quot;>20% off MedicAlert membership and 10% off all products </span><br />when using the code SENIORS at the checkout.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-12&quot;>\r\n<div id=&quot;first&quot; class=&quot;onethird text-left&quot;>Redeem this<br /> special offer in<br /> 2 easy steps:</div>\r\n<div id=&qu