urn safely to their loved ones in an emergency. <u>Learn more about our Safe Return program. <internal link></u></p>',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,999,'NDIS',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2017-03-29 17:30:42','2017-03-29 07:04:49','2017-03-29 17:34:47'),(301,770,6,0,0,'NDIS','MedicAlert&reg; Foundation is a registered NDIS provider',NULL,'ndis',0,'<p>We are proud to be a registered National Disability Insurance Scheme (NDIS) provider. The NDIS is the Federal Government&rsquo;s new way of providing individualised support for eligible people with permanent and significant disability, their families and carers.</p>\r\n<p>This means your <a href=&quot;/benefits-of-membership&quot;>MedicAlert membership</a> and an <a href=&quot;/products/everyday&quot;>everyday ID</a> may be covered as part of your NDIS plan.</p>\r\n<p>MedicAlert offers an internationally recognised low risk and low cost service, with products that give you or your loved one a greater independence within their community and ensure their health conditions are easily communicated through their ID and accessible MedicAlert electronic health record.</p>','<h3>MedicAlert and NDIS participants may be able to receive the following covered by the NDIA:</h3>\r\n<div class=&quot;row&quot;>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-4 text-center&quot;><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/1.png&quot; alt=&quot;ID&quot; />\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;>ID</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-4 text-center&quot;><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/2.png&quot; alt=&quot;ID&quot; />\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;>Membership</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-4 text-center&quot;><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/3.png&quot; alt=&quot;ID&quot; />\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;>Delivery</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-3 text-center&quot;> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n