> </p>\r\n<p>When a first responder calls our Safe Return Service we can:</p>\r\n<ul style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;>\r\n<li>Provide them with up to date and relevant information about the member&#039;s medical history.</li>\r\n<li>Relay critical information about previous wandering history.</li>\r\n<li>Deliver information on the member&#039;s condition and the best way to approach them.</li>\r\n<li>Alert the next of kin, if needed.</li>\r\n<li>Help make sure that your loved one is returned home quickly and safely.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>As Australia&rsquo;s most trusted and recognised provider of medical ID&rsquo;s, MedicAlert Foundation can provide you and your loved ones with full support in an emergency. From the moment they join MedicAlert, they&rsquo;ll gain access to a range of <a style=&quot;background-color: #ffffff;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.medicalert.org.au/benefits-of-membership&quot;>exclusive benefits</a>.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>For only $80* you can have peace of mind for your loved ones knowing they&#039;re protected when it matters the most. To redeem this offer, simply select a MedicAlert ID style below and follow the prompts to the checkout.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note: our Safe Return program may also be covered by the NDIS. If you have an existing plan, please <a href=&quot;https://www.medicalert.org.au/ndis&quot;>register with your NDIS details</a>. </strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; style=&quot;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/autismlogo.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;autismlogo.jpg (78 KB)&quot; width=&quot;780&quot; height=&quot;180&quot; /></p>','<h2>For just $80* you will receive the following:</h2>\r\n<p>The choice of one of the medical IDs shown below, one year of MedicAlert membership, free postage and a membership card holder.</p>\r\n<p>*Offer valued at up to $123</p>\r\n<div class=&quot;row&quot;>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-3 text-cent