rd and supported by the 24/7 emergency response service.</strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>If you want to re-order a product when you renew your membership, you can view your past purchases and re-order or review an ID.</p>\r\n<p><a class=&quot;btn btn-red&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 10px;&quot; href=&quot;/my-purchases&quot;>My purchases</a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,99,'Quick Renew - Renew Your Membership in One Step | MedicAlert',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,'2016-09-21 14:52:10','2018-03-06 06:33:00',NULL),(343,603,2,0,17,'&#039;What Matters To You&#039; Competition Winners',NULL,NULL,'what-matters-to-you-competition-winners',0,'Thank you to everyone who entered our &#039;What Matters To You&#039; competition! ','<div id=&quot;description&quot; class=&quot;news-description&quot;>\r\n<p>Thank you to everyone who entered our &#039;What Matters To You&#039; competition! We had just over 600 entries and it was very difficult trying to decide on only 6 winners. The winners are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nerida Robinson, NSW</li>\r\n<li>Sharryn Shaw, VIC</li>\r\n<li>Michael Welden, SA</li>\r\n<li>Jeremy Ko, NSW</li>\r\n<li>Lola Mudie, QLD</li>\r\n<li>Graham Connolly, WA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>CONGRATULATIONS to our winners! Your gift certificates will be posted out to you this week.</p>\r\n</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,999,'&#039;What Matters To You&#039; Competition Winners',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,'/uploads/news-and-resources/images/medic-alert-logo.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2013-11-01','2020-12-31',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2016-10-03 11:26:54','2018-07-26 05:05:30','2018-07-26 14:35:30'),(344,830,6,0,0,'St Johns Offer','St Johns Offer',NULL,'stjohns',0,'<div>\r\n<h1><span class=&quot;highlight&quot;>Benevolent offer</span><br /><span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>St Johns</span></h1>\r\n<span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>Free one year MedicAlert<sup>&reg;</sup> membership</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>and choice of a selected MedicAlert ID </span></div>\r\n<p><a class=&quot;btn btn-red&quot; title=&quot;Benefits of membership&quot; href=&quot;#products&quot;>Choose product</a></p>','<p>MedicAlert&reg; Foundation is passionate about making sure support is available to all Australians living with a health or medical condition. If your child has a health condition, allergy or takes regular medication, a MedicAlert membership can provide peace of mind for you and your family. If you received a promotional flyer at a recent SA Schools First Aid Training facilitated by St Johns, your child qualifies for our benevolent package.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>A MedicAlert ID can help to communicate your children&rsquo;s health needs if you&rsquo;re not around and protect them by providing family, friends, teachers and healthcare professionals with the ability to quickly recognise medical or health conditions in the case of an emergency.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>As a member, they&rsquo;ll also gain access to a range of exclusive member benefits, unlimited updates to membership and fridge cards listing health details, and a secure electronic health record that can be updated online at any time to include any new or relevant health information.</p>','<h2>Offer includes:</h2>\r\n<p>A one year MedicAlert<sup>&reg;</sup> membership and your choice of one of the MedicAlert IDs shown below with free postage.</p>\r\n<p>*Offer valued at up to $123</p>\r\n<div class=&quot;row&quot;>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-4 text-center&quot;><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/1.png&quot; alt=&quot;Medical ID&quot; />\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;>MedicAlert ID</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-4 text-center&quot;><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/2.png&quot; alt=&quot;Medical ID&quot; />\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;>Membership</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=&quot;col-sm-4 text-center&quot;><img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/3.png&quot; alt=&quot;Medical ID&quot; />\r\n<div class=&quot;cost-text&quot;>Postage</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','<p>*Selected products only. Price includes standard postage and handling and an Australia MedicAlert Foundation product warranty. Offer extended to those who attended an SA Schools First Aid Training facilitated by St Johns and may be subject to authentication.</p>',NULL,'STJOHNS',788,NULL,NULL,0,999,'St Johns Offer',NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,0,'/uploads/Header%20images/benevolent-landing-page.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,'2018-05-07 09:28:14','2018-07-24 23:53:39',NULL),(345,841,1,0,0,'Employee Wellbeing Program','Employee Wellbeing Program',NULL,'employee-wellbeing',0,'<div>\r\n<h1><span class=&quot;highlight&quot;>EMPLOYEE WELLBEING</span><br /> PROGRAM</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>Protect your employees</span><br /><span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;> in and out of the workplace</span><br /><span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>with MedicAlert.</span></div>\r\n<p><a class=&quot;btn btn-red&quot; title=&quot;Contact us&quot; href=&quot;#contact&quot;>Contact us</a></p>','<h2>Employee Wellbeing Program</h2>\r\n<p>MedicAlert&#039;s genuine IDs and Emergency Response Service can provide your employees with protection in and out of the workplace.</p>\r\n<p>Once members have joined, they will have access to their personalised ID and wallet card, as well as an electronic health record, able to be updated on our website and stored on our secure database.</p>\r\n<p>This database facilitates our lifesaving 24/7 Emergency Response Service, which  can be accessed by emergency personnel and health professionals at any time and contains additional information on a member&#039;s medical or health conditions, medication, emergency contacts and special needs.</p>','<h3>Benefits of membership</h3>\r\n<p>Only MedicAlert can provide your team with full support in an emergency and keep them protected in the